body.description: Kleenex Ultra Soft Facial Tissues are soft 3-layer tissues blending indulgent softness with dependable strength. Designed for runny noses and watery eyes, Ultra Soft 3-ply tissues provide a perfect balance of unbeatable softness and strength to comfort skin and help protect your hands. This pack of tissues contains 8 flat boxes with 120 facial tissues per box. America’s softest Ultra tissue (among national brands) is also the #1 preferred Ultra tissue (vs. Ultra national brands). Kleenex Ultra Soft tissue boxes feature a variety of colors and designs that complement your home decor. Stay stocked up on tissues during cold & flu, allergy, and back-to-school seasons. Skip the store and have Kleenex Ultra Soft facial tissues delivered!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Kleenex Ultra Soft Facial Tissues have been an absolute game-changer in my daily routine. With a pack of 8 containing a total of 960 tissues, this product has exceeded my expectations in every way. These tissues are incredibly soft and gentle on the skin, making them a must-have for anyone with sensitive skin like mine.Having used various tissue brands in the past, I can confidently say that Kleenex Ultra Soft Facial Tissues stand out from the rest. They are not only soft but also strong and durable. Whether it's for wiping away tears, cleaning up spills, or just for everyday use, these tissues have proven to be reliable in every situation.One of the aspects I appreciate the most about these tissues is their convenient packaging. The compact size of each tissue box makes it easy to carry around in my bag or place in different rooms of the house. Plus, with 120 tissues per box, they last much longer than other brands, saving me frequent trips to the store.I also love that Kleenex offers this product in a pack of 8, ensuring that I always have an ample supply on hand. It's a cost-effective option that not only saves money but also reduces the need for frequent reordering.In conclusion, Kleenex Ultra Soft Facial Tissues have become an indispensable part of my daily life. Their softness, durability, and convenient packaging have won me over completely. I highly recommend these tissues to anyone looking for a reliable and gentle solution for all their tissue needs. They have certainly made a positive difference in my life, and I couldn't be happier with my purchase.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars It's Kleenex. What bad things can be said about it?
reviews.reviewText: Biggest plus is that it's the Kleenex brand at a reasonable per-unit price. In the past, when I have tried to save money, the generic versions ripped my nose apart. The price increase to Kleenex from generic is well worth the in-tact skin around my nose.Second is that this quantity is just the right size. I can easily store it in my limited living space, and it lasts the whole of cold/flu/allergy season. Granted, I am shopping for one, but this one-and-done deal can't be beat.The only negative I have is that it took forever for it to arrive. We're talking the span of over a month. And the box was very beat-up. Not sure if it's because of the shipper making a mistake, or Kleenex dropping the ball somehow. If it wasn't for this, it would have been five stars.Nevertheless, it's a solid brand, a solid quantity, and fantastic price.
